                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6475" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0448</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8900 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一览Offer派：专业技术人才招聘的独门秘籍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yilan’s Offer Party: A Special Way to Recruiting Professionals</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">施丹，张鸣，游子晴，肖恬宁，杜思赟，张爱武</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中农业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市一览网络股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">专业技术人才；就业服务机构；招聘渠道与方法；个人—组织匹配；匹配动态性；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Professionals; Employment service agencies; Recruitment channels and methods; Person-Organization fit; Dynamic matching</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着“中国制造2025”战略不断推进和我国产业转型升级的现实需求，企业对专业技术人才的竞争日趋激烈，就业服务机构提供的中高端人才寻访服务日益受到用人方的青睐。本案例介绍了深圳市一览网络股份有限公司首创的一款向企业提供专业技术人才快速上岗解决方案的招聘产品Offer派。主要描述了该产品的缘起、优化与实施流程，并以小王与B企业牵手的故事为例，详细介绍了Offer派帮助企业获取专业技术人才的过程。通过案例分析，使学生了解招聘渠道和常见方法，比较外部招聘渠道各方法的优劣势；理解提高招聘效果的个人—组织匹配原则，分析就业服务机构实现求职者与企业匹配的具体方法；并在此基础上理解求职者个人—组织匹配动态性，思考如何在招聘过程中增强求职者的感知匹配以促进其接受企业入职邀请；最后，引导学生进一步思考人才在进入组织后，应如何通过人力资源管理实践来提高个人—组织匹配质量，以实现人力资本价值增值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With implementing the “Made in China 2025” strategy and China’s industrial upgrading, competition for attracting professionals among enterprises has become increasingly fierce. More and more employers hire talents through employment service agencies’ efforts. This case introduces the Offer Party, a recruiting product invented by Shenzhen Yilan Network Co., Ltd, which helps clients to fill technical positions quickly. The case reviews the Offer Party’s introduction, optimization and implementation. Take Xiao Wang’s story as an example, it introduces the process how the Offer Party runs. The case aims to guide learners to understand the main recruitment channels and common methods and compare the pros and cons of outside sources of candidates. It also helps learners to understand the benefits of person-organization fit and explore hiring practices for person-organization fit. Additionally, it leads learners to understand the development of applicant person-organization fit perceptions during the recruitment process and discuss how to increase applicants fit and influence their final job choice. Finally, it leads learners to think about how to improve the quality of person-organization fit through human resource management practices and create human capital-based value after applicants enter the organization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《员工招聘》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外部招聘渠道及优劣势；个人-组织匹配理论；基于个人-组织匹配的招聘步骤；招聘过程中求职者个人-组织四配的动态变化；人力资本的动态；匹配模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
